SPK_0: of what happened with Newton.

94
00:05:54,650 --> 00:05:56,710
SPK_0: Or how did science actually...

95
00:05:56,750 --> 00:06:00,210
SPK_0: And he said, look, science did not actually get born

96
00:06:00,210 --> 00:06:02,010
SPK_0: on the basis of finding truth.

97
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:05,210
SPK_0: Science was born on the basis of accruing power

98
00:06:05,210 --> 00:06:06,990
SPK_0: to a certain class of people

99
