00:06:54,710 --> 00:06:56,370
SPK_0: And they can deploy resources.

120
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,450
SPK_0: They strategically have...

121
00:06:58,450 --> 00:06:59,470
SPK_0: They have strategic capacity.

122
00:06:59,690 --> 00:07:01,110
SPK_0: There's still a lot of strategic...

