SPK_1: but have you thought about these consequences?

154
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:56,070
SPK_1: Have you thought about this?

155
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,230
SPK_1: That's why we completely misunderstand

156
00:07:57,230 --> 00:07:58,650
